<h2><strong>CADmeister2020 Version Upgrade (CAD)</strong></h2><h3><strong>&bull; Improved workability &bull;</strong></h3><h4><strong>1. Improved Semi-Transparent Shading</strong></h4><p>-&nbsp;Upgraded the Drawing Algorithm.</p><p>- Released a command to set transmittance rate.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAD/CADmeister2020_CAD_1.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>2. Coordinate Axis Handle</strong></h4><p>-&nbsp;A function to adjust the Coordinate Axis Handle was added.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAD/CADmeister2020_CAD_2.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>3. Unload Work Environment files</strong></h4><p>-&nbsp;Release a command to clear work environment.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAD/CADmeister2020_CAD_3.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>4. Add &lsquo;the Same Location as the Drawing Origin OBJ&rsquo; to the Saving Destination</strong></h4><p><strong>-&nbsp;</strong>Add the &lsquo;same location as the original OBJ&rsquo; option to the default saving locations.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAD/CADmeister2020_CAD_4.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>&bull; 3D Promotion&nbsp;&bull;</strong></h3><h4><strong>5. Support STEP Conversion AP242</strong></h4><p><strong>-&nbsp;</strong>Enabled a STEP conversion function to support a conversion of AP242 data.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAD/CADmeister2020_CAD_5.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>6. Support CATIA Shape Set ASSY</strong></h4><p>-&nbsp;Enabled the functions to support the situation where CATIAv5 input functions do not convert Assembly data.</p><p>- The functions can convert Assembly Component data into group strata.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAD/CADmeister2020_CAD_6.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>7. General-Purpose Input GU (GenerationUnit)</strong></h4><p><strong>-&nbsp;</strong>Released GU (Generation Unit), a new method to specify historical data as an input subject.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAD/CADmeister2020_CAD_7.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>8. Improved Denotation</strong></h4><p>-&nbsp;Denotation scales can be kept even after changing a view direction.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAD/CADmeister2020_CAD_8.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>9. Move&amp;Copy</strong></h4><p><strong>-&nbsp;</strong>Enhanced the &ldquo;Move&amp;Copy&rdquo; command with &lsquo;Coordinate Axis&rsquo;,the capability to help adjusting figures.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAD/CADmeister2020_CAD_9.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>10. Improved Angle Constraint of &ldquo;HistoryPlacement_Place&rdquo; Command</strong></h4><p>-&nbsp;Enabled plus/minus (＋/- )indications for values of placement condition, Angle.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAD/CADmeister2020_CAD_10.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>11. StandardPart_CreateManipulate</strong></h4><p>-&nbsp;Added formula unction to &lsquo;Family Tables&rsquo; item in the &ldquo;StandardPart_Create&amp;Manipulate&rdquo; command window.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAD/CADmeister2020_CAD_11.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>12. Display Shape Evaluation Results</strong></h4><p>-&nbsp;Added a histogram function for evaluation results</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAD/CADmeister2020_CAD_12.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>13. Coordination with Excel Spreadsheets</strong></h4><p>-&nbsp;Released an add-on function to position parts.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAD/CADmeister2020_CAD_13.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>-&nbsp;Add a function to position buttons.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAD/CADmeister2020_CAD_13.2.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>14. Easy_Sketch/Rigid Body Operations</strong></h4><p><strong>-&nbsp;</strong>Released a command to repurpose constrained shapes and use them as sketch data without compromising the sizes nor constraints.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAD/CADmeister2020_CAD_14.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>15. Easy_Wire/Roll Wires</strong></h4><p><strong>-&nbsp;</strong>Release a command to project line/curve data on a cylindrical surface as if wrapping a line/curve around the cylinder.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAD/CADmeister2020_CAD_15.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>16. Easy_Wire in general</strong></h4><p><strong>-&nbsp;</strong>Update &ldquo;Pnt_2LineDistance&rdquo; command and &ldquo;Change dimension&rdquo; command.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAD/CADmeister2020_CAD_16.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>17. Offset _ Along the Surface</strong></h4><p>- Enhance by updating command window to include [specifying multiple member surfaces] function as well as &nbsp;&ldquo;VariableOffset&rdquo; command and &ldquo;Unification&rdquo; command.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAD/CADmeister2020_CAD_17.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>18. Easy_Modeling ／ DeleteSolidHoles</strong></h4><p><strong>-&nbsp;</strong>Released a function to collectively fill solid holes</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAD/CADmeister2020_CAD_18.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>19. Easy_Modeling ／ 2StepExtendedSurface</strong></h4><p><strong>-&nbsp;</strong>Release a function to create a new surface by extending boundary curves/lines of external periphery.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAD/CADmeister2020_CAD_19.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>20. Improved Easy_Modeling</strong></h4><p>-&nbsp;Improve commands related to infinite surface, separation, sloping/drafting, fillet and trim surface</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAD/CADmeister2020_CAD_20.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>21. PlaceParts / DefineAssembleConstraint</strong></h4><p>-&nbsp;Released the &ldquo;PlaceParts/Middle-Point Constraint&rdquo; command.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAD/CADmeister2020_CAD_21.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>22. Direct_Deformer / HoleBoss Detach</strong></h4><p>-&nbsp;Released a function to identify holes and bosses as independent solids from a shape.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAD/CADmeister2020_CAD_22.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>&bull; 3D Data utilization area expansion&nbsp;&bull;</strong></h3><h4><strong>23. Work Scenes Supporting&nbsp;Layer and Advanced context Menu</strong></h4><p>-&nbsp;Add layer file and advanced input menu to the registration items.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAD/CADmeister2020_CAD_23.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>24. Easy_Drafting : Supporting 3D Symbols on an Arbitrary Plane</strong></h4><p><strong>-&nbsp;</strong>Released an add-on function to create 3D symbols on an arbitrary plane.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAD/CADmeister2020_CAD_24.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>&bull; New product &bull;</strong></h3><h4><strong>25. 3DAviewmeister</strong></h4><p>-&nbsp;The exclusive viewer for on-site will be released. (November 2020 Schedule)</p><p>- It is capable of enabling confirmation and assignment of 3DA (PMI and attributes) data.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/CADmeister2020/CAD/CADmeister2020_CAD_25.PNG" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p>